                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-1214" type="surname" value="ALDERMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-1214" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM ALDERMAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant H</hi> 7.) I went after the prisoner, and saw him in Crispin-street—I took him—the duplicate of this necklace was sent to the prosecutor, and I got the necklace.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
